case_title: ROSHAN AND OTHERS vs RABIA BIBI AND OTHERS
legal_basis: Section 13 of the Consolidation of Holdings Ordinance 1960

case_summary.restoration_arguments: Counsel for petitioners argued for restoration of the case.

land_dispute_details.respondent_claim: Land given to respondents' father illegally during consolidation.

case_summary.collector_action: Case remanded to Consolidation Officer for spot visit and mutual compromise or proposals.
case_summary.appeal_dismissal_reason: Additional Commissioner (Cons.) deemed the appeal rightly dismissed.

final_decision: No interference with the impugned order; revision petition dismissed.
